  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bae\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9c\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "US Secretary of State arrives in Sri Lanka",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka, which is facing a major economic crisis, is seeking additional cooperation from friendly countries.",
        "In this case, US President Joe Biden has announced that he will provide 20 million dollars for the food security of the country in order to reflect that the US is paying more attention to the crisis in Sri Lanka.",
        "President Biden made the announcement while attending the G-20 summit.",
        "Similarly, Sri Lankan Ambassador Mahinda Samarasinghe in Washington along with President Biden and Secretary of State Anthony Blinken also met.",
        "Ambassador Mahinda Samarasinghe mentioned that Sri Lanka's demands and expectations have been positively responded to during those meetings.",
        "At the same time, a high-level delegation including US Treasury Deputy Assistant Secretary for Asia Robert Kaproth and Deputy Assistant Secretary for South and Central Asian Affairs Kelly Geideling visited Sri Lanka last week and participated in various meetings.",
        "During this, they discussed a wide range of issues including Sri Lanka-US joint projects to recover from the economic crisis and expansion of cooperation.",
        "An important official of the government mentioned that important announcements may be made regarding US cooperation for Sri Lanka as the team has now returned to Washington.",
        "At the same time, he also mentioned that the date of State Secretary Anthony Blinken's visit to Sri Lanka may be announced as soon as possible."
      ],
